metadata.name: Phoenix Rising
metadata.description:
All there is there was before,
And shall remain forever more.

Ash to ash, dust to dust,
All that once shone had turned to rust.
The aftermath of greed and lust. 

Oh will they never learn?
The world around them burns…

And winds of change 
now fan those flames.

As the Phoenix rises from the ashes.

All there is there was before,
And shall remain forever more. 

Let’s turn the page
To start this lore. 

— The Great Awakening
